# Portfolio design system

## Layout
- Page max width: 1120px (`--page-max`, `--max-width`)
- Text column max: 760px (`--text-column-max`)
- 12-column grid for split sections on case pages
- Section spacing: `padding-block: 120px` for major sections (`--section-padding`)
- No stacking multiple vertical paddings

## Typography
- H1: 48–56px desktop (enterprise presence)
- H2: 36–40px
- Body: 18px / 1.6
- Meta: 14–15px muted (`--color-meta`)
- Accent: `#E87722` (`--color-accent`)

## Strict bans (do not reintroduce)
- No case numbers on home preview cards (no 01/02/03/04, no ghost numbers, no year above number)
- No decorative ghost typography or watermark numbers
- No repeated identical cards or duplicated metadata
- No long paragraph > 3 lines
- No random background stripes
- No decorative dividers or extra typography experiments on case pages
- No "dribbble-style" decorative layout

## Surfaces
- Base background: `#F6F6F4` (`--color-bg-page`)
- Surfaces (cards, impact section): white only (`--color-bg-white`)

## Home case preview structure (CaseRow)
- Left: TITLE · POSITIONING (1 line) · META (single line, muted) · OUTCOME STRIP (bold) · CTA "View case →"
- Right: single media block (16:9, rounded 20px, subtle shadow)
- No numbers. No tags line. Same system for all cases.

## Case pages (e.g. Banking)
- Hero: eyebrow, H1, description (max 2 lines), meta row (4 columns), hero media 16:9 rounded 24px, caption 14px
- Context: split layout; left narrative, right metric rows (large % accent, title, subline)
- Role: 3 equal columns (Owned / Influenced / Decided), clean bullets, no column numbers
- Before/After: slider, placeholder images, caption
- Design work: split blocks (1 sentence + media), no duplicate captions
- Validation: short paragraph, inline chips, media right
- Impact: white surface, 3-column KPI grid, no extra paragraph
